  "rationale": "<p>Distribute the negative sign: 6x\u00b2 + 11x \u2212 4 \u2212 2x\u00b2 \u2212 3x + 9 = (6x\u00b2 \u2212 2x\u00b2) + (11x \u2212 3x) + (\u22124 + 9) = 4x\u00b2 + 8x + 5. Choice (a) is correct.</p>",
